<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to <%= process.env.APP_NAME %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-title {
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .getting-started {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #1976d2;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Welcome to <%= process.env.APP_NAME %>!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for joining our platform! We're excited to have you on board and can't wait to help you get started.</p>
        
        <div class="getting-started">
            <h2>Getting Started</h2>
            <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Complete your profile</li>
                <li>Generate your first API key</li>
                <li>Check out our documentation</li>
                <li>Try our interactive API console</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3 class="feature-title">Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Powerful API endpoints</li>
                <li>Real-time data access</li>
                <li>Comprehensive documentation</li>
                <li>24/7 support</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Need help getting started? Check out our resources:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/docs">Documentation</a></li>
            <li><a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/tutorials">Tutorials</a></li>
            <li><a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/api-reference">API Reference</a></li>
            <li><a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/support">Support Center</a></li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="social-links">
            <p>Connect with us:</p>
            <a href="<%= process.env.TWITTER_URL %>">Twitter</a>
            <a href="<%= process.env.GITHUB_URL %>">GitHub</a>
            <a href="<%= process.env.LINKEDIN_URL %>">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="<%= process.env.DISCORD_URL %>">Discord</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by <%= process.env.APP_NAME %></p>
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= process.env.COMPANY_NAME %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <%= process.env.SUPPORT_EMAIL %></p>
            <p>
                <small>
                    You're receiving this email because you recently created an account on <%= process.env.APP_NAME %>.
                    If this wasn't you, please <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/support">contact us</a>.
                </small>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 